<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="auth-page">
    <div class="glass-panel auth-card">
        <div class="auth-header">
            <!-- Simulated logo icon -->
            <div class="user-avatar" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; font-size: 1.6rem; margin: 0 auto 16px auto; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--kpru-green) 0%, var(--kpru-gold) 100%);">
                LPC
            </div>
            <h2>ระบบจองห้องประชุม</h2>
            <p>ศูนย์การเรียนรู้ตลอดชีวิตและพัฒนามาตรฐานวิชาชีพ (LPC)</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--kpru-green); margin-top: 4px;">https://asl.kpru.ac.th/lpc/</p>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="auth-error">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i> <%= error %>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <form action="/login" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email" class="form-label">อีเมลผู้ใช้งาน (KPRU Email)</label>
                <div style="position: relative;">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope" style="position: absolute; left: 16px; top: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary);"></i>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="เช่น user@kpru.ac.th" style="padding-left: 44px;" required>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
                <label for="password" class="form-label">รหัสผ่าน</label>
                <div style="position: relative;">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-lock" style="position: absolute; left: 16px; top: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary);"></i>
                    <input type="password" id="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="ระบุรหัสผ่านของคุณ" style="padding-left: 44px;" required>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100" style="padding: 14px;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-right-to-bracket"></i> เข้าสู่ระบบ
            </button>
        </form>

        <div class="auth-links">
            <span style="color: var(--text-secondary);">ยังไม่มีบัญชีผู้ใช้?</span> 
            <a href="/register">ลงทะเบียนผู้ใช้ใหม่</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Testing accounts info box -->
        <div class="glass-panel" style="margin-top: 24px; padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 0.8rem; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--kpru-gold); font-size: 0.85rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i> ข้อมูลบัญชีสำหรับทดสอบระบบ</h4>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0; color: var(--text-secondary); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;">
                <li><strong>Admin:</strong> admin@kpru.ac.th (pw: admin1234)</li>
                <li><strong>Approver:</strong> approver@kpru.ac.th (pw: approver1234)</li>
                <li><strong>User:</strong> user@kpru.ac.th (pw: user1234)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
